pr_title: Added Sorting , Grid view for storage units

pr_body: - Added a line in readme mentioning to activate virtual environemt
1) Added move to storage units with click on Airavata logo or Storage units option in Left Navigation Bar

pr_title: Added sort by Last Modified for storage units
pr_body: Currently sorting of storage units is available only Name and Size , Added sorting by Last Modified Date

pr_body:
1. Improved Documentation for resolving general errors 
2. Improved Documentation for turning on the dev server

pr_title: Added and Modified Vue components for dashboard
pr_body:
Made the following changes as per New MFT dashboard design
1 ) Modified  Vue Component and developed UI for displaying storage units 
2 ) Added Vue Component and developed UI for displaying Transfers 
3) Added Vue Component and developed UI  for adding new storage unit 
4) Added Vue component for initiating transfer between storage units 
( UI for file browsing and transfer initiation is yet to be  done ) 
5) Added Django integration for the above mentioned Vue components
